{"tid":51470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪話搭車唔坐得 企係班蝗側邊都影衰我","createTime":"2016-12-23T09:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T09:11:08.000Z","uid":2766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1be6485c97ffee5498a4ca359fcd61930bcbee13","tid":51470,"uid":2766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我呢就企緊西鐵<br />\n有個蝗家庭入左車廂<br />\n見到有行坐位既小情侶側邊有個超窄位<br />\n係超窄呀 我半邊身都入唔到呀<br />\n個蝗媽死要個女硬塞入去<br />\n本身個蝗囡都有羞恥心 企佢老母硬迫佢去<br />\n搞到對情侶都唔係幾敢坐<br />\n我企係側邊都淆晒底怕混爲一員<br />\n唯有迫於無奈講下一站元朗 下一站元朗<br />\n<br />\n總結 內地狗真係好撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcfec8b170b20cb96cb11192e3b70b971807544","tid":51470,"uid":48099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"其實好多蝗蟲都幾大體味，又口臭。"},{"pid":"cd7fe8553a5bcdf3366c9e944834fdb2de89a3c6","tid":51470,"uid":2766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多蝗蟲都幾大體味，又口臭。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔怕羞個下先天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c6bb2071e4aec8b01a59573e741d48d21baf41","tid":51470,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"內乜撚嘢地"}]}